com.igormaznitsa.prol.logic
Interface ProlMappedObjectSearcher

public interface ProlMappedObjectSearcher

The interface desribes a class which can be used for search of a mapped object for a string key. The key is the text of a Term object.

Author:
Igor Maznitsa (igor.maznitsa@igormaznitsa.com)
